    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2983718/" class="title-link">一遍一遍地走过，一次一次地忘记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2983718"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lydy/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1364551-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lydy/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">当归莳子</span>
